          "content": "• Branding label: fade-in 200ms ease-out, opacity 0 → 0.6\n• Spinner ring: rotate(360deg) 1s linear infinite\n  - Track: #1E2744 stroke 6px | Arc: #00FF88 stroke 6px\n  - 120px diameter — larger breathing room on desktop\n  - Poker chip emoji centered, static (no rotation)\n• Loading dots: staggered opacity pulse 800ms loop\n  - Dot 1: full opacity, Dot 2: 50%, Dot 3: 20%\n  - Each cycles 200ms apart (200ms stagger)\n• Text group: fade-in 300ms ease-out (200ms after spinner)\n• Entire screen: crossfade to session view < 500ms\n• prefers-reduced-motion: spinner static, no dots, instant text",
