    {
      "type": "frame",
      "id": "AddStoryModalAnnot",
      "x": 2000,
      "y": 9530,
      "name": "annotAddStoryModal",
      "width": 560,
      "fill": "#1A1F3A",
      "cornerRadius": 6,
      "layout": "vertical",
      "gap": 8,
      "padding": 16,
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "AddStoryAnnotTitle",
          "fill": "#FF006E",
          "content": "ADD STORY MODAL — COMPONENT SPECS",
          "fontFamily": "Bricolage Grotesque",
          "fontSize": 11,
          "fontWeight": "900"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "AddStoryAnnotDesc",
          "fill": "#9CA3AF",
          "content": "BACKDROP:\n• bg-poker-bg-page/80 + backdrop-blur-sm\n• fixed inset-0 z-50\n• click backdrop → onClose()\n\nCARD ANIMATION (Framer Motion):\n• initial: scale 0.96, opacity 0\n• animate: scale 1.0, opacity 1\n• exit: scale 0.96, opacity 0\n• transition: spring stiffness 300, damping 20\n• prefers-reduced-motion: duration 0, opacity only\n\nCARD LAYOUT:\n• bg-poker-bg-header (#1E2744)\n• rounded-[4px], w-full max-w-[480px]\n• mx-4 p-6 flex flex-col gap-5\n\nHEADER ROW:\n• Title: 14px/black/tracking-widest/text-poker-magenta\n• Close: Button variant=ghost size=sm, calls onClose\n\nDIVIDER: h-[1px] bg-poker-bg-row\n\nFIELD LABELS: 11px/black/tracking-widest/text-poker-green\n• STORY ID: maxLength 20, placeholder 'e.g. MIC-100'\n• TITLE: maxLength 80, placeholder 'As a user, I can...'\n\nFOOTER BUTTONS:\n• CANCEL: variant=ghost size=md → onClose\n• + ADD STORY: variant=primary size=md type=submit\n• Disabled when either field is empty\n\nBEHAVIOUR:\n• Escape key → onClose\n• Form submit → onSubmit(storyId, title) + reset\n• stopPropagation on card click",
          "fontFamily": "Bricolage Grotesque",
          "fontSize": 10,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "frame",
      "id": "VotMob3Annot",
      "x": 1590,
      "y": 3793,
      "name": "annotVotMob3",
